name: Cele, Etherym of the Gate
text: 2 Sea Serpent monsters you take no damage from battles involving this monster or the monsters this card points to. This card cannot be targeted for attack if it is pointing to an Etherym monster. You can only use the following effects of "Cele, Etherym of the Gate" once per turn. If an Etherym monster is sent to the GY, you can add 1 Etherym spell/trap that's banished or in the GY to your hand. If an Etherym monster is banished, you can return 1 card your opponent controls back to their hand. If a banished Etherym monster you own is special summoned, you can special summon 1 Sea Serpent from your hand or GY.
